[thinking] **Considering metadata generation**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I’m thinking about whether tests should generate metadata using an agent. For Native Image by default, it seems tests might rely on agent-generated metadata. I suppose we just need to add the tests, but it’s possible that executing a native image requires reachability metadata for test helper classes. Since dynamic access goes from the library to test classes, it’s interesting to consider if the user code filter includes only javassist. I wonder how the agent condition could impact metadata creation.
[thinking] 
