 discovery and method metadata helpers.\n  - Covers instance method invocation via `ClassMetaobject.invoke`.\n- Updated `JavassistTest` to make the top-level test class `public`, matching repository test rules.\n\nI did not run compile or tests, per instruction.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_067a9ceeb697fbe30169f8e3a52b4c8195bbf45a6257108481\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1530, "output": 992, "cacheRead": 24576, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 27098, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1777918870180, "responseId": "resp_067a9ceeb697fbe30169f8e396b3f48195ba5b438f3ad82300"}}
